{"type": "article", "id": 51496, "title": "长途旅行，你需要这款能当枕头的眼罩｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-26T23:10:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 48736, "name": "Lagom Bath"}, {"id": 16057, "name": "Norm Architects"}, {"id": 48737, "name": "Matt Benedetto"}, {"id": 48738, "name": "Deepanjan Sinha"}, {"id": 48739, "name": "Narbeh Khoygani"}, {"id": 48740, "name": "Tomonori Tanaka"}, {"id": 40160, "name": "Visibility"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 211, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180326181157gmCVD96F4rueS8Bz.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Minimal Collection by Norm Architects for Lagom Bath</h3><p>丹麦事务所 Norm Architects 为韩国品牌 Lagom Bath 创造了一系列极简主义风格的浴室柜和配件，专门设计用于面积较小的小型住宅和公寓。整个系列包括浴室柜、卷纸架、毛巾架和挂钩。</p><p>这款浴室柜有垂直独立式和水平壁挂式两个版本，可在水槽顶部放置木制托盘以存放产品，另有带滑动镜门的壁挂式水平、垂直储物柜。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181233rRm0tbiQa8OkDUIN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181234kA5mbKBsOjaMWgZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181237YXvpoNZQujI0bszA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181238Id24XkTP3izyE0fQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334602\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://normcph.com/front-gallery/lagom-bath-x-norm-architects-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Norm Architects</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Bent Boxes by Visibility for Normann Copenhagen</h3><p>纽约设计二人组 Visibility 为丹麦家居设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 设计了 2018 年新品 Bent 盒子。据称设计师的灵感源自日本传统的弯曲薄板圆饭盒（Magewappa）。这种盒子可以堆叠存储，让用户自行决定使用它们的方式，既可以作为托盘使用，也可以堆叠成收纳盒使用。售价 65 美元，<a href=\"https://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/bent-box?v=356959\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181402GsVz9JEnxlZLt2Hw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181404SsKM6uPNlhzL78yI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.406879\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181539mK1dLSc4Z5qQVURh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803261815409wLan1HRoIcC0NGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181620072ghWJ6oXwHGymD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647143\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Picklestone by Tomonori Tanaka</h3><p>吃日本料理时主食主菜旁边，通常都放着各种经过腌渍的萝卜、小黄瓜等小菜。日本设计师、美食家 Tomonori Tanaka 去年尝试自己动手作渍物，没想到却面临不少难题，比如腌渍用的容器大小，压实渍物的均匀力度，以及渍物的美观程度等等。</p><p>最终，Tomonori Tanaka 发觉现有腌渍用的工具无法负荷他的需求，于是决定干脆自己设计腌渍用的工具。Picklestone 就是其提出的解决方案，只要将蔬菜和腌渍用的调味料放入瓶子中，然后把柏木盖子盖上，最后再放上压石，接下来就是等待渍物随着时间逐渐发酵、入味。售价 130 美元，<a href=\"https://shop.spoon-tamago.com/collections/new/products/picklestone\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181734LMv5SGm4BuUzCOEf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181736D057q4SmPALd9EFt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181736voInMNfr8t4R6GqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181736KioHzlFk8Y1PqngM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181736ZBuUNKgT0YPJODL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181736PazVckC8RuMpHi7h.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666071\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MyKee 2.0 by Narbeh Khoygani</h3><p>拆快递用钥匙已经是常见手段了。但设计师 Narbeh Khoygani 却针对钥匙进行了大改造，将其变身为拥有 20 项功能的便携多功能工具 MyKee 2.0。</p><p>它保留了钥匙的框架造型，但是细节方面加入了许多小细节，最上边的中空部分可以用来拧螺丝，10 毫米、8 毫米、5 毫米三种规格的螺丝钉都可以操作。除此之外，钥匙的顶端也有一个小缺口，能卡住螺丝刀等。它还能割绳子，起啤酒盖，开易拉罐，甚至用它到头的部分去死皮，用锯齿的部分修指甲。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0614z1g4h5&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803261819404FMvlhx8zNb0onR7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181941gtk3y0M6zcIwoS2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181943u5L2pw4Bv7yxzYtA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326181945CTug3f2cIrZNm7Ue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/03/23/the-new-and-improved-multi-tool/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Plus (earphones) and Nest (speaker) by Deepanjan Sinha</h3><p>设计师 Deepanjan Sinha 推出了一个将耳机与音箱融合在一起的概念设计。他构想的产品叫做“+Plus”（耳机）和Nest（音箱）。Nest 音箱既能用于收纳耳机，又能为耳机无线充电。</p><p>设计师设想的使用场景是，假如你正通过耳机听音乐，回到家里取下耳机，将其放置在 Nest 上，那么音乐会自动切换到扬声器上。这样就实现了无缝切换音乐。+Plus 耳机可以快速套在手腕上，和口袋、包里的其他杂物分隔开来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182020Om3wMhVAb5DgtxcX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803261820203NvPlGoaJV0t5fQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182021isyL5X0pDbYkCQdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.043810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182021HtMNPTSfoBuklgDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182021XRVpFOTI4J3tybPq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182021ztOTMKqlPSe7BJ8Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182023ytuJc2PHp41rYqR8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/03/22/a-speaker-and-headphones-in-harmony/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Voyage Pillow by Matt Benedetto</h3><p>Voyage Pillow 是一款集眼罩和枕头于一身的旅行枕，出自设计师 Matt Benedetto 之手。最近他在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上推出了这个项目，试图解决长途旅行者的困扰。</p><p>Voyage Pillow 正面较窄的部分是眼罩，而背面则是个厚实的枕头。表面是纯棉材质，触感柔软，让人能舒适地进入睡眠状态。当眼罩使用时，它正好可包裹住眼睛，后仰睡觉正好靠在枕头上。枕头部分还可以侧靠在窗子上，完全不担心脖子会受伤。</p><p>更重要的是，Voyage Pillow 的体积非常小巧，还不到一般 U形枕一半的体积，便于携带。早鸟价 21 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sondretravel/voyage-pillow-the-most-versatile-and-compact-trave?ref=ev0hkq\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182111dX5QwGmKxVonPDcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182112eyLhwvf2XqVolOkz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182111RixZrsYkpvUwj0TN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182112Utni2omRGyEb04Z3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803261821120eVpZvyHLt6EsM7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182112qI2E4oBZedQLkzT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180326182112Kf7ezk8jJqTNCMYo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}